<view class='bg-gradual-blue padding radius text-center shadow-blur title_css page'>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top action" hidden="{{hidden_or_not}}">
    <view class="flex padding justify-between">
      <text class='text-red'></text>更新说明（点击右侧关闭）
    </view>
    <view class="flex padding justify-between">
      <button class="cu-btn lines-red round shadow sm" bindtap="close_it">
        <view class="icon-close text-red"></view>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last' hidden="{{hidden_or_not}}">
    <view class='text-sm'>v2.0.0 （2019.07.27）</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>1. 默写练习改为选择练习，加快学习节奏。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>2. 将所有词库移至云端，极大地减少了小程序的体积。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>3. 支持动词变位反查。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>4. 增加法语特殊字符软键盘（仅在软键盘收起时有效，正查仍不受大小写和特殊字符影响）。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>5. 删除和修改了帮助页面的内容。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>6. 增加了赞赏页面，感谢大家的支持。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>具体内容请参见 https://uniquelab.cn/conj-helper-2-0-0</view>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow sm' bindtap="copy">点击复制网址</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-mauve light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-mauve'></text>关于法语动词变位记忆小助手
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="help">📄使用帮助</button>
        <button class='cu-btn lines-blue round shadow' open-type="feedback">❌报错和建议</button>
      </view>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="like_me">✨赞赏支持我</button>
        <button class='cu-btn lines-blue round shadow' bindtap="copy">😻我的主页</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-grey light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-grey'></text>基础设置
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <!-- 用户 openid style="background-image: url({{avatarUrl}})" -->
    <button open-type="getUserInfo" bindgetuserinfo="onGetUserInfo" class="cu-btn lines-red round shadow" bindtap="onGetOpenid">{{tongbu}}</button>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>点击上方登陆，登陆之后您的所有设置和卡片将会和云端自动同步。</view>
    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>时间选择</view>
      <picker bindchange="PickerChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{picker}}">
        <view class="picker">
          {{index?picker[index]:'单位：秒'}}
        </view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>更改“分类记忆→倒计时”的时间。单位：秒。默认10秒。</view>
  </view>


  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-red'></text>单词设置
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>

    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>50基础动词（共50词）</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked1_50}}" bindchange="words_50" />
    </view>

    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>100进阶动词（共50词）</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked1_100}}" bindchange="words_100" />
    </view>

    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>230高手动词（共130词）</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked1_230}}" bindchange="words_230" />
    </view>

    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>典型精选</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked1_selected}}" bindchange="words_selected" />
    </view>

    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>典型动词（不建议勾选）</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked1}}" bindchange="extra_words" />
    </view>

    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>请选择对应的背词范围。各选项动词不重叠。典型动词（不建议勾选）有许多非常用动词，故不建议勾选。</view>
  </view>


  <view class="cu-bar bg-blue light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-blue'></text>时态设置
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>进阶时态</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked2}}" bindchange="advanced_shitai" />
    </view>
    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>高手时态</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked3}}" bindchange="extra_shitai" />
    </view>
    <view class="cu-form-group margin-top">
      <view class='title'>不常用时态</view>
      <switch checked="{{isChecked4}}" bindchange="inusuel_shitai" />
    </view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>默认的常用时态包括了直陈式复合过去时、直陈式现在时、直陈式简单将来时；</view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>进阶时态包括了直陈式未完成过去时、直陈式愈过去时、直陈式先将来时；</view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>高手时态包括了条件式现在时、条件式过去时、虚拟式现在时、虚拟式过去时；</view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>非常用时态包括了直陈式简单过去时、直陈式先过去时。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-red'></text>小程序推荐
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class='text-sm'>👇试试我的其他小程序👇</view>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="hard_choice">艰难的选择</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>